    "body": "set the size option in `new-window` handler:\r\n\r\n```\r\nwin.webContents.on('new-window', function (evt, url, frameName, disposition, options, additionalFeatures) {\r\n        if(options.width == 800 && options.height == 600){ //default size is 800x600\r\n            let {width, height} = electron.screen.getPrimaryDisplay().workAreaSize;\r\n            options.width = width * 0.9 | 0;\r\n            options.height = height * 0.9 | 0;\r\n        }\r\n});\r\n```"
